            <title>小米米家 IH 电饭煲 2 预售：0 氟涂层内胆，首发价 349 元起</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/929/154.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/929/154.htm</guid>
